## Security Issues to be fixed:

- No Rate Limiting

Login endpoint vulnerable to brute force
Fix: Add rate limiting (next-rate-limit, upstash/ratelimit)

- [ ] No CSRF Protection Beyond SameSite

SameSite: 'lax' helps but isn't foolproof
Fix: Add CSRF tokens for sensitive mutations

- [ ] Missing Account Lockout

No protection after N failed login attempts
Fix: Track failed attempts, lock account temporarily

